        "logic": "var calc_output=[];\n\nvar age_raw = parseFloat(age);\nvar sex = parseFloat(sex);\nvar cci_raw = parseFloat(diabetes)+parseFloat(cpd)+parseFloat(kidney)+parseFloat(pvd)+parseFloat(chf)+parseFloat(dementia)+parseFloat(cancer)+parseFloat(stroke)+parseFloat(liver)+parseFloat(heart_attack)+parseFloat(ulcer)+parseFloat(paralysis)+parseFloat(aids)+parseFloat(rheum);\n\nif (parseFloat(pvd) ==1 || parseFloat(heart_attack) ==1){\n  var history=0.267265312;\n}\nif (parseFloat(pvd) ==0 && parseFloat(heart_attack) ==0){\n  var history=0;\n}\n\nif (age_raw >=20 && age_raw <=49){\n  age = -2.228678713;\n}\nif (age_raw >=50 && age_raw <=54){\n  age = 0;\n}\nif (age_raw >=55 && age_raw <=59){\n  age = 0.400599289;\n}\nif (age_raw >=60 && age_raw <=64){\n  age = 0.941322019;\n}\nif (age_raw >=65 && age_raw <=69){\n  age = 1.295007128;\n}\nif (age_raw >=70 && age_raw <=74){\n  age = 1.629533438;\n}\nif (age_raw >=75 && age_raw <=79){\n  age = 1.763345763;\n}\nif (age_raw >=80 && age_raw <=89){\n  age = 1.927443543;\n}\nif (age_raw >=90){\n  age = 2.018752269;\n}\n\nif (age_raw <85){\n\tif (cci_raw==0){\n  \tvar cci=0;\n\t}\n\tif (cci_raw>=1 && cci_raw<=3){\n \tvar cci=0.612122574;\n\t}\n\tif (cci_raw>=4 && cci_raw<=5){\n\t  var cci=0.82507284;\n\t}\n\tif (cci_raw>=6 && cci_raw<=9){\n\t  var cci=0.956099733;\n\t}\n\tif (cci_raw>=10){\n\t  var cci=1.395164653;\n\t}\n}\n\nif (age_raw >=85){\n  var cci = 1.529325519;\n}\n\n\nvar coefficient_sum = age + sex + cci + history - 4.216058062;\nvar or_calc = Math.exp(coefficient_sum);\nvar risk_raw = (or_calc/(1 + or_calc))*100;\n\nvar risk = risk_raw.toFixed(1);\n\nvar odds_raw = 1/(risk_raw/100);\nvar odds = odds_raw.toFixed(0);\n\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: risk,\n\tvalue_text:'% risk of death',\n    message: ''\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'VACO Index',\n    value: risk,\n    value_text:'% risk of death',\n    message: ''\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Percentile',\n    value: '1 in '+odds+' chance of dying',\n    value_text:'',\n    message: ''\n});\n",
